Miss Even, My Little Heat Stroke: Let&#39;s parse this out: 120 words appear in your letter. 97 are about Old Boyfriend. A mere 23 concern New Boyfriend. Add one four-legged. Total it with words No. 6, No. 7, No. 8, No. 9, and No. 10 (where you answer your own question by beginning your correspondence with &quot;The love of my life...&quot;). Come on, do you really need Auntie Eeee?

This letter is from the Ask E. Jean Archive, 1993-2017. Send questions to E. Jean at E.Jean@AskEJean.com.
